comments.body:
Issue was due to the fact that the Eucalyptus version differed from the ENABLED CLC, Walrus machine versus the NC machine.  Difference is as follows:

*NC package version*

{code}
eucalyptus-nc-3.2.1-0.0.568.20130228git99339836.el6.x86_64
{code}

*CLC, Walrus package version*

{code}
eucalyptus-cloud.x86_64 0:3.2.1-0.0.562.20130228gita15631d1.el6
{code}

Even though they were both 3.2.1, they were the _exact_ same versions.  Putting in a feature request so that when someone installs Eucalyptus to make sure all Eucalyptus versions are the same before components can be registered.
